          "valueCode": "unknown"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "purpose": "(Clinical Focus: All non-branded prescribable medication formulations in RxNorm except those limited to ingredient only.),(Data Element Scope: Medication orderables),(Inclusion Criteria: Prescribable medications including multiple ingredient medications.\nUnion(FilterOnProperty(TTY,SCDG), FilterOnProperty(TTY,SCDF), FilterOnProperty(TTY,SCD), FilterOnProperty(TTY,GPCK),\nFilterOnProperty(TTY,SCDC))),(Exclusion Criteria: Concepts for proprietary representations of drugs. Non-prescribable (OTC) drugs. Ingredient formulations.)",
